Clone groups via GroupBuilder copy constructor in
TypicalPersons.getTypicalAddressBook and
TypicalGroups.getTypicalAddressBook to prevent cross-AddressBook
aliasing caused by shared static Group instances. Each AddressBook
now receives independent Group objects with their own
UniquePersonList, avoiding shared mutation of group membership.
